snippet.title: CBBC: SKID the Scrambling Squirrel online game (2002)
snippet.description:
Help SKID find her missing supply of Autumn acorns by avoiding all the obstacles and crows controlling him with the arrow keys.

An original Flash game taken from their Really Wild Show webpage.
